1. *Piva* se učestalo konzumira u našim krajevima. (Beer is frequently consumed in our regions.)
2. On je voleo da *piva* pivo sa svojim prijateljima. (He liked to drink beer with his friends.)
3. Često bi se našli na terasi i *pivali* uživo muziku. (They would often find themselves on the terrace, drinking and playing live music.)
4. Naši prijatelji su imali naviku da *pive* kažu neke smešne viceve. (Our friends had the habit of drinking and telling some funny jokes.)
5. Ona je pozvala prijatelje na kućnu zabavu i svi su *pili* pivo. (She invited her friends for a house party and they all drank beer.)